    <stitle>BRAKE COMPONENTS: This Service Manual Section should be used for reference only. For more current service
        information on all components go to the Bendix website from the ISIS Suppliers menu and refer to the Service
        Data Sheets. - AIR COMPRESSOR GOVERNOR (TYPE D-2) - CLEAN AND INSPECT
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
        <title>CLEAN AND INSPECT</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Clean metal parts in cleaning solvent. Dry parts with compressed air.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Wipe rubber parts with a clean, dry cloth.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Inspect body for cracks or other damage. Be particularly careful that the body air passages,
                the filters, exhaust stem and piston are not obstructed.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Check springs for cracks, distortion or corrosion.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Replace all parts not considered serviceable.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
